                  <img class="thumb-image" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5afead0c506fbe072ef6c2f7/fae2be28-df15-4b62-816a-17d9b7a79d62/C.png" data-image-dimensions="1999x1065" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" data-image-id="62b9c4df1ae64509f2f684c0" data-type="image" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5afead0c506fbe072ef6c2f7/fae2be28-df15-4b62-816a-17d9b7a79d62/C.png?format=1000w" />
                
            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Steps lowered back to 150, skip_steps at 60. <br>Lowering eta to 0.6 and clamp_max to 0.035.<br>Increasing cut_ic_pow from 10 to 20.</p>



































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                  <img class="thumb-image" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5afead0c506fbe072ef6c2f7/5faf1e3b-c71d-4494-85cf-71fd0f544516/J.png" data-image-dimensions="1386x724" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" data-image-id="62b9c4f850e8055ee0b39e45" data-type="image" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5afead0c506fbe072ef6c2f7/5faf1e3b-c71d-4494-85cf-71fd0f544516/J.png?format=1000w" />
                
            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  

































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
