        </figure>]]></description></item><item><title>3dtotal Interview</title><category>2D</category><category>3D</category><dc:creator>Andrei Cristea</dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jun 2016 13:18:00 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.undoz.com/blog/2016/6/8/3dtotal-interview.html</link><guid isPermaLink="false">5afead0c506fbe072ef6c2f7:5afead6f124f1c1116b47aba:5afead6f124f1c1116b47adb</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>3DTotal republished the interview I did for 3DCreative Magazine.&nbsp;You can check it out <a target="_blank" href="http://www.3dtotal.com/interview/814-interview-with-andrei-cristea-by-3dtotal-staff-eve-online-ccp-games">HERE</a>&nbsp;.</p>



































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          <a class="
                sqs-block-image-link
                
          
        
              " href="http://www.3dtotal.com/interview/814-interview-with-andrei-cristea-by-3dtotal-staff-eve-online-ccp-games" target="_blank"
          >
            
          
            
                
                  <img class="thumb-image" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5afead0c506fbe072ef6c2f7/1526826618049-MU92CT5K3QMDS5TTB1ST/3d_total_interview.jpg" data-image-dimensions="640x847" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="3d_total_interview.jpg" data-load="false" data-image-id="5b01863f758d46bedb0792d9" data-type="image" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5afead0c506fbe072ef6c2f7/1526826618049-MU92CT5K3QMDS5TTB1ST/3d_total_interview.jpg?format=1000w" />
                
            
          
        
